&lt;h1 id="wave-properties-in-cold-unmagnetized-plasma"&gt;
 Wave Properties in Cold Unmagnetized Plasma
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#wave-properties-in-cold-unmagnetized-plasma"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before we can get to the wave properties, we first need to be specific about what we mean by a &amp;ldquo;cold&amp;rdquo; plasma. In the fluid formulation, we have a few central equations:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Cold Magnetized Plasma Dispersion Relation</title><link>https://peppyhare.github.io/r/notes/UWAA556/ch02-3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://peppyhare.github.io/r/notes/UWAA556/ch02-3/</guid><description>&lt;span&gt;
